{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">PURSUED</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You are on the run from the police for a Crime You didn't commit.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Drive for as long as You can without getting caught.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Closer they are, and the more of them there are, the more Your wanted level goes up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If You get Arrested, You have to Start back at the Beginning!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use Bullet-Time during crashes for a Cool Effect.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Additionally, here are the features and content a customer can expect to be included with their purchase . . .</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Insane Car Physics</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Deformable Car Destruction (Except for the player car)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You have to drive as long as You can without getting arrested</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Closer the police are, and the more of them there are, the more Your wanted level goes up, so, keep Your distance</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">If You get arrested, You have to start back at the beginning, so, don't get caught</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You can use Bullet-Time during crashes to see all of the details</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">What is the Highest Score You can Get?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Can You find ALL of the &quot;Easter Eggs&quot;?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">* NOTE: This game uses Unreal 5.5, Make sure You have the latest GPU/Video Drivers Installed. *</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3360390/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733472153","